headline.main: Waratahs Suffer Double Injury Blow Before Lions Clash
headline.print_headline: Waratahs Suffer Double Injury Blow Before Lions Clash

lead_paragraph: An Oregon family that lost six people, including five children, in a fatal fire will donate the organs of the mother and her 13-year-old son.
